			<span>e</span> 
		</h3>
		<ul id="nav_list">
			<li> 
				<a href="/rain_barrel/water_usage" class="wl-link selected">
					<strong> Water Usage History <br/> </strong>
					<small> Stats, conservation & logs </small>
				</a>
			</li>
			<li> 
				<a href="/rain_barrel/water_quality" class="wq-link">
					<strong> Water Quality <br/></strong>
					<small> Stats & explanations </small>
				</a>
			</li>
			<li> 
				<a href="/rain_barrel/filter_life" class="fl-link">
